OL,3,CTrial date set for prisoner charged
OL,4,Cwith murdering Soham killer Ian Huntley
OL,6,FA trial date has been set for an
OL,7,Finmate charged with the prison murder
OL,8,Fof Soham killer Ian Huntley.
OL,10,FAnthony Russell, 44, appeared at
OL,11,FNewcastle Crown Court by videolink
OL,12,Ffrom HMP Frankland, near Durham, on
OL,13,FWednesday (3 June 2026) for a brief
OL,14,Fhearing during which he did not enter
OL,15,Fa plea.
OL,17,FRussell is charged with a single
OL,18,Foffence of murdering 52-year-old
OL,19,FHuntley, who was allegedly attacked
OL,20,Finside the maximum security jail in
OL,21,FFebruary.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/3
