CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F429A1780665075
OL,3,CTrial date set for prisoner charged
OL,4,Cwith murdering Soham killer Ian Huntley
OL,6,FHuntley was taken to the Royal
OL,7,FVictoria Infirmary in Newcastle, where
OL,8,Fhe died on 7 March.
OL,10,FThe judge set a trial date for 23
OL,11,FNovember, with a further pre-trial
OL,12,Fhearing in July.
OL,14,FHuntley had been serving a life
OL,15,Fsentence for the murders of 10-year-
OL,16,Folds Holly Wells and Jessica Chapman.
OL,18,FThe ex-school caretaker killed the
OL,19,Fbest friends after they left a family
OL,20,Fbarbecue to buy sweets in Soham,
OL,21,FCambridgeshire, in 2002.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/3
