PN,42903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F429A1780665075
OL,3,CTrial date set for prisoner charged
OL,4,Cwith murdering Soham killer Ian Huntley
OL,6,FHe dumped their bodies in a ditch 10
OL,7,Fmiles away. They were not found for 13
OL,8,Fdays despite a search involving
OL,9,Fhundreds of police officers
OL,11,F.At the time, Huntley lived with
OL,12,FMaxine Carr who was a teaching
OL,13,Fassistant at Holly and Jessica's
OL,14,Fprimary school.
OL,16,FHe denied murdering the girls but was
OL,17,Fconvicted after a trial at the Old
OL,18,FBailey in 2003. He was jailed for life
OL,19,Fwith a recommended minimum term of 40
OL,20,Fyears.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/3
